window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A love that spans centuries. A choice that could change everything.</p> <p>Newly married and adjusting to life in the past, Dr. Abigail Thorne has built a home with Captain Ben Turner in colonial America. But when a visit from her twin brother stirs old emotions, Abigail proposes a bold idea—one that will take her and Ben back to the future for a visit.</p> <p>Ben has fought battles before, but none quite like this. The modern world is a dazzling whirlwind of wonders, but he fears it may be too enticing for Abigail to leave behind again. As they navigate a place where past and future collide, old doubts resurface, and new possibilities emerge. Will their love stand the test of time, or will returning to the future unravel the life they’ve fought to build?</p> <p>If you love heartfelt time-travel romance with endearing characters, emotional depth, and a touch of humor, Bridges Across Time will transport you on an unforgettable journey.</p> <p>Start listening today and discover a love story that defies the centuries.</p>"; 
